# Classify the message by subject — bug-report arm. Guarded on
# `@ticket.category == ""` so a higher-priority match at scope 100
# (account-access) wins. See 100/account-access.txcl for why this is
# EMIT and why the arms are laddered across scopes.
WHEN @ticket.category == "" && @lmtp.msg.subject =~ /(?i)bug|crash|broken|error/
  EMIT @ticket.category = "bug_report",
       @ticket.priority = "normal"
